Signature, Title and Inscription

life_date: John M. Whitehead, Photographer, Scottish, c. 1864–1949
signed: on mount front, under where LL edge of sheet was when attached, in pencil: [THE DARKNESS DEEPENS. (underscored)]; in pencil: [#819]; in blue; [5th Annual/ -5 1/2-]
title: The Darkness Deepens
